{"tid":2412810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國名宿：02年世界盃我是故意爆頭馬爾蒂尼","createTime":"2021-02-18T08:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T09:13:06.000Z","uid":29969,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b99cb90f9ee2609b01f98aabc7ff2b5548d928b7","tid":2412810,"uid":29969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:52:51.000Z","msg":"在日前綜藝節目中，李天秀談了自己為何要爆頭馬爾蒂尼：&ldquo;那些意大利球員很囂張，他們目中無人，我感覺他們看不起韓國球員，而且有韓國球員在那場比賽中已經被踢傷了。  &rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n &ldquo;我踢的那個人叫馬爾蒂尼，他和洪明甫位置相似，都是隊長。我踢他，並不因為他是馬爾蒂尼，而是因為他恰好在那裡。&rdquo;李天秀繼續說道。"},{"pid":"4e84149518dd4cf515d6e8c2c30cd1495d0af631","tid":2412810,"uid":29969,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hB1Xe0J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhB1Xe0J.png&h=a6259ef0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35b594981593a19e77962dd3c3d55b326224086c","tid":2412810,"uid":29969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OmhO57s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOmhO57s.gif&h=ef25497c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"149b7e0a0785b95ca689627e8fa0c7721a39cbe8","tid":2412810,"uid":124156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:54:38.000Z","msg":"垃圾賤種韓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e71ad81d64f36ed661cc6e587c17f51d564d60","tid":2412810,"uid":76063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:54:40.000Z","msg":"呢班韓狗仲夠膽提"},{"pid":"2be7753c13bafb9f72f046fe6f0817a201b94e37","tid":2412810,"uid":36724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88e71ad81d64f36ed661cc6e587c17f51d564d60","tid":2412810,"uid":76063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:54:40.000Z","msg":"呢班韓狗仲夠膽提"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T08:56:39.000Z","msg":"殿軍已袋"},{"pid":"7afae60b621e525da6b9